news.headline: D-Wave Advantage2 Quantum Computer Now Available For US Government applications At Davidson Headquarters
D-Wave Advantage2 Quantum Computer Now Available for U.S. Government Applications at Davidson Technologies
news.summary: PALO ALTO, Calif. & HUNTSVILLE, Ala., November 03, 2025--D-Wave Quantum Inc.
